ployment Runbook\\n\\n**System:** Kalshi Arbitrage Engine (Phase 4)  \\n**Author
:** Liam (SRE)  \\n**Task:** T354  \\n**Date:** 2026-04-03\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Quic
